1
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:26,300
♪The gentle breeze leaves no trace♪

2
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:29,670
♪It stirs the old times♪

3
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:33,560
♪Love is gained and lost♪

4
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:37,370
♪Only then does it become unforgettable♪

5
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:41,370
♪The bamboo leaves
are rustling and falling♪

6
00:00:41,370 --> 00:00:44,770
♪Fate is delayed and scattered♪

7
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:48,840
♪Only lingering hatred remains♪

8
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:51,210
♪Echoing♪

9
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,130
♪Old dreams are like illusions♪

10
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:59,490
♪Alas, the world is too indifferent♪

11
00:00:59,490 --> 00:01:01,760
♪If there were no obsession♪

12
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:05,870
♪I wouldn't be thinking of someone♪

13
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:09,630
♪If it's destined to be alone♪

14
00:01:09,630 --> 00:01:13,310
♪Like a snowstorm♪

15
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:15,980
♪When love and hate dissolve♪

16
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:20,940
♪Only a long gaze remains♪

17
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:25,610
♪A drop of tear♪

18
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:29,490
♪Falls, burning my heart♪

19
00:01:29,490 --> 00:01:33,340
♪We loved without regret♪

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,580
=My Destined Consort=

21
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:39,620
=Episode 21=

22
00:01:40,330 --> 00:01:41,720
I'll take you out to play next time,

23
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,640
alright?

24
00:01:42,790 --> 00:01:44,470
- Congrats, My Lord.
- Congrats, My Lord.

25
00:01:44,470 --> 00:01:45,310
Thank you.

26
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:47,040
My family finally has an heir.

27
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,760
It's truly comforting.

28
00:01:51,610 --> 00:01:52,470
Indeed.

29
00:01:52,470 --> 00:01:53,830
You're truly blessed.

30
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:55,120
How fortunate.

31
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,960
Yanyan?

32
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,720
Yanyan?

33
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:16,830
Yanyan?

34
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,800
Yanyan?

35
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,470
Don't worry. In the Prefect's Mansion,

36
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,960
he'll definitely be safe.

37
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,670
Let's split up.

38
00:02:23,670 --> 00:02:24,640
I'll go that way.

39
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,870
Then I'll go this way.

40
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,520
- Yanyan?
- Yanyan?

41
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,150
Yanyan,

42
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,590
why are you here alone?

43
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,750
Who are you?

44
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,750
I'm your mother's younger sister.

45
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,240
You should call me Aunt.

46
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,550
Are you catching fireflies?

47
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,520
Let me help you.

48
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:47,990
Yanyan?

49
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:51,390
Yanyan?

50
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,640
Yanyan?

51
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,520
Let me catch one for you.

52
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,640
Look at this.

53
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:00,480
Yanyan?

54
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,240
- Yanyan?
- Yanyan?

55
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,030
Look over there.

56
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,480
Shall we catch that one?

57
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,150
Come on.

58
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:11,270
Yanyan?

59
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,240
Yanyan!

60
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,590
Yanyan!

61
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,520
Shen Qilan, you...

62
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:29,830
Go on.

63
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:32,520
Mother.

64
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,630
Yanyan,

65
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,310
didn't I tell you not to run off?

66
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:38,870
I was just catching fireflies with Aunt.

67
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,430
Don't worry, Jiangli.

68
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,710
A firefly flew toward the lake just now.

69
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:51,870
Come here.

70
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,590
Yanyan.

71
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,240
You mustn't run off again.

72
00:03:57,470 --> 00:03:58,550
If we can't find you,

73
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,920
your mother will be worried.

74
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,430
I will remember.

75
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:03,670
Good boy.

76
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,470
Jiangli, you're truly fortunate

77
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:07,870
to have married such a fine man
as Master Jingming.

78
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,600
Even after so long apart,

79
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,990
he still treats Yanyan like his son.

80
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,550
You're getting insolent.

81
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,640
Yanyan is my son.

82
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,150
Please don't be offended,
Master Jingming.

83
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:20,390
Sorry for speaking out of turn.

84
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,080
But

85
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,510
Jiangli suddenly brought back a child,

86
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,630
and you just believed her?

87
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:27,280
Shen Qilan, you...

88
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,940
So, this is the kind of manners

89
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,160
they teach

90
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,550
at Master Jingxiu's Mansion.

91
00:04:33,010 --> 00:04:35,040
Yanyan, how about I take you
to see the fireworks?

92
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,160
Fireworks!

93
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,040
I want to see fireworks!

94
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,960
Let's go.

95
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,390
Shen Qilan,

96
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,680
if you dare to harm Yanyan,

97
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,510
I won't let you go.

98
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,950
Jiangli, what are you worried about?

99
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,040
I'm Yanyan's aunt, after all.

100
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,680
You can't run off again.

101
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,760
Do you hear me?

102
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,070
Yes.

103
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:12,950
Yanyan,

104
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,550
come here. Let me hold you.

105
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,550
Grandfather, Grandmother.

106
00:05:17,550 --> 00:05:18,470
Good boy.

107
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,070
How are you so adorable?

108
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,310
- Look.
- Look.

109
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:28,960
Isn't it beautiful?

110
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:29,990
So beautiful!

111
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,720
So pretty!

112
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,790
- Look at this.
- Do you like it?

113
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,200
It's stunning!

114
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,120
Look!

115
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,200
Isn't it beautiful?

116
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,840
That one is beautiful too.

117
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:47,770
♪The wind and moon
fall through our fingers♪

118
00:05:47,770 --> 00:05:51,010
♪Like a dream that will return
to the starry night♪

119
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,480
So beautiful.

120
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:57,580
♪Turning into cycles flowing in time♪

121
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,040
So pretty.

122
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,680
That one's the highest.

123
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:08,240
Do you like it?

124
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,200
Yes.

125
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,480
Mr. Chu, why don't you go over there?

126
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,310
The view's better on that side.

127
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,840
The view

128
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:24,160
doesn't matter.

129
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,040
What matters is being with family.

130
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,040
If you're alone,

131
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,630
it doesn't matter where you watch from.

132
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,640
Go on.

133
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,310
Your family is over there.

134
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:45,430
I have other things to do after this.

135
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,240
I'll have to leave for a while.

136
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,720
Where are you going?

137
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,870
When will you leave?

138
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,950
And when will you be back?

139
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,680
You're asking me
so many questions at once.

140
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,280
I don't know how to answer you.

141
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,720
Then start from the beginning.

142
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,680
Mr. Chu,

143
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,430
when you return,

144
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,950
will you watch the fireworks

145
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,480
with me again?

146
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,560
Great.

147
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,600
Yanyan has finally

148
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,680
been acknowledged this time.

149
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:47,070
Now I don't have to worry
about slipping up.

150
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,760
Yanyan has finally returned

151
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,390
to his rightful family.

152
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:53,830
But

153
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,800
I don't think Jingxiu

154
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:57,480
is happy about this.

155
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,230
The Prefect's eldest grandson

156
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:00,830
is Jingming's son.

157
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,800
How could he be happy?

158
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,570
Let's not talk about that.

159
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,950
Do you remember

160
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,230
that Jingming and Jiangli

161
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,750
told us not to tell anyone?

162
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,750
We were so afraid of slipping up

163
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,630
that we fled Dongzhou in the night.

164
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,270
Of course.

165
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,040
If we had stayed back then,

166
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,820
with how loose our tongues are,

167
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,870
we definitely would've
let something slip.

168
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,990
It's okay now. Everyone's happy.

169
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,640
Let's drink.

170
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,360
- Here.
- Cheers.

171
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,040
Master Jingxiu,

172
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:52,320
don't let today's events trouble you.

173
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,040
This wine

174
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,960
needs to be savored slowly.

175
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,720
Relax, Master Jingxiu.

176
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,910
We'll have children

177
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,320
sooner or later.

178
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:16,990
Besides,

179
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:19,080
this child may now be

180
00:09:19,570 --> 00:09:21,790
a strength to Master Jingming,

181
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,480
but perhaps someday,

182
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,630
he'll become a blade pointed at him.

183
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,120
Do you have a plan?

184
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:37,670
A plan? Not really.

185
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,520
But that is

186
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,630
how the world works.

187
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,270
The way of heaven avoids fullness.

188
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:43,800
Excessive prosperity leads to decline.

189
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,670
The time

190
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,680
for the fire to die out

191
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,200
is near.

192
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,630
Good wine.

193
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,440
What's on your mind?

194
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,270
In ten days,

195
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:09,150
it'll be Mr. Song's initiation ceremony.

196
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,670
Yanyan

197
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,990
will formally become his disciple.

198
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,200
It should be a happy occasion,

199
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,910
but I just can't shake this unease.

200
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,470
Think about it.

201
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,400
Now that Mother and Father

202
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,960
have acknowledged Yanyan,

203
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:26,960
that means from now on,

204
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:29,360
he'll have the Lu family backing him up.

205
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:31,840
So surely, only good things will happen,

206
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,510
nothing bad.

207
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,510
Don't overthink it.

208
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,600
Get some rest.

209
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:43,300
(Master Jingming's Mansion)

210
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,280
Yunyi.

211
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:46,600
I think Master Jingming
and Consort Jiangli

212
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:48,480
are already deeply in love.

213
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,380
Yanyan's identity
has also been confirmed.

214
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,320
It's time.

215
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,240
Yunyi, I'm still nervous.

216
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,670
I think Miss Yulan

217
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:11,910
is gentle, graceful,

218
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,790
and skilled in martial arts.

219
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,480
She's a perfect match for you.

220
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,320
You are

221
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,270
a dignified man,

222
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,310
Master Jingming's trusted aide,

223
00:11:22,310 --> 00:11:24,080
and our mansion's second-best fighter.

224
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:26,240
You have nothing to be afraid of.

225
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,080
Miss Yulan

226
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,630
is already waiting.

227
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,960
Yunyi,

228
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,120
how well you know

229
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,040
about romance.

230
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,560
Are you here

231
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:46,110
to see Master Jingming?

232
00:11:46,550 --> 00:11:47,510
No.

233
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:48,910
Are you here

234
00:11:48,910 --> 00:11:49,870
to see Consort Jiangli?

235
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,670
No.

236
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,400
Who are you here to see?

237
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:56,750
You.

238
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:58,750
Me? What for?

239
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,240
There is indeed something

240
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,990
I wish to tell you.

241
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,440
We've known each other

242
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:05,630
for a while now.

243
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,670
I'm sure you have some idea

244
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,870
of my character and conduct.

245
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,790
Well, I don't, actually.

246
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,500
There's no time then.

247
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,440
You...

248
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,080
Are you here to borrow money from me?

249
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,960
No. Please don't misunderstand.

250
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,750
You scared me.

251
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,710
Come on.

252
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,910
What's this?

253
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,840
I wonder if you know my feelings.

254
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,850
Jiangli once said to me:

255
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:41,830
When mountains crumble,

256
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:42,760
rivers run dry,

257
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:44,670
thunder rumbles in winter,
snow falls in summer,

258
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:45,710
and heaven and earth unite,

259
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:47,220
only then would I part with you.

260
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,080
"Part with you"?

261
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,080
What do you think?

262
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,670
She said she has someone she likes.

263
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,400
It's okay.

264
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,870
There are plenty of flowers
in the world.

265
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:16,270
No need to cling to just one.

266
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,200
Romantic things are just too hard.

267
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,320
She recited a poem to my face,

268
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,270
but the poem was for someone else.

269
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:35,260
(Master Jingming's Mansion)

270
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:38,080
Father, Mother, hurry up!

271
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,950
It's my big day today.

272
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:47,600
We can't be late.

273
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:49,390
You're acting so serious about it.

274
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:50,880
Yanyan,

275
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:52,660
have you memorized
the Encouraging Learning

276
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:53,580
I've been teaching you?

277
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:54,470
Father,

278
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:56,790
I can recite it now.

279
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,270
Good boy. Let's go.

280
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:06,220
(Master Jingming's Mansion)

281
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:10,030
Mother, I want a candied hawthorn.

282
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:11,470
Yanyan,

283
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,560
how about later?

284
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:13,870
After class,

285
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,720
I'll get you the whole bunch, okay?

286
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,720
It's a deal then.

287
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:22,240
- Let's make a pinky promise.
- Let's make a pinky promise.

288
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,550
- Come on.
- Let's go.

