00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,920
Xuan, don't be afraid.

579
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,230
Everything's fine, Xuan.

580
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:57,550
I'm here.

581
00:25:57,830 --> 00:25:59,800
How could she prove it any more clearly?

582
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:02,910
If Yanyan weren't her son,

583
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:05,230
how could she risk her life
to protect him?

584
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:10,070
Yanyan...

585
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,640
Is Yanyan

586
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,870
really not our grandson after all?

587
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,150
The people I sent
to Pei Village yesterday

588
00:26:16,150 --> 00:26:17,150
came back today.

589
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,840
Everything they found

590
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,600
matches Qingniang's story.

591
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,760
Jingming.

592
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,680
With all the evidence in front of us,

593
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:29,630
how am I supposed to believe you?

594
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:33,070
Father,

595
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:34,520
if Jiangli

596
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,470
had taken that test,

597
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:38,320
I'm sure she would've done the same.

598
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,800
She came back despite the danger

599
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:42,920
just to get the Lei Pill

600
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,910
and save Yanyan's life.

601
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,040
Back then,

602
00:26:48,270 --> 00:26:50,150
you and Jiangli came to me
for the Lei Pill.

603
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:51,520
Was it to save Yanyan?

604
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:53,120
Yes.

605
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,430
She went through so much.

606
00:26:55,830 --> 00:26:56,910
I was with her

607
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,390
every step of the way.

608
00:26:58,680 --> 00:26:59,640
Father,

609
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,030
please give me more time.

610
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:02,150
I'll uncover the truth

611
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,520
down to the last detail.

612
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:06,880
Fine.

613
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,390
You have three more days.

614
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:10,880
Yes.

615
00:27:18,960 --> 00:27:19,920
How frustrating.

616
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:21,550
Yanyan looks just like Jingming

617
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:23,520
when he was a child.

618
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,000
How could he not be our grandson?

619
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,230
I also hope Yanyan

620
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:32,280
is our grandson.

621
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,160
Oh, my.

622
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,280
This work never ends.

623
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:37,990
Excuse me, you two.

624
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:40,040
May I ask something?

625
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:41,630
Is there someone named Qingniang here?

626
00:27:42,260 --> 00:27:43,150
- Yes.
- That's right.

627
00:27:43,150 --> 00:27:44,230
What do you need from her?

628
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,200
I heard

629
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,080
she had a daughter, right?

630
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,150
A daughter?

631
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:52,230
I remember she had a son.

632
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:54,560
They say he's got a round face
and big eyes.

633
00:27:54,820 --> 00:27:55,680
Qingniang treasures

634
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,150
her son dearly.

635
00:27:58,030 --> 00:27:59,470
Then may I ask

636
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,520
if you know where he is now?

637
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:03,840
I heard her son was taken.

638
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:05,390
She's been searching for him.

639
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,960
What do you need from her?

640
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:12,880
Who's asking for her?

641
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:14,000
No, nothing.

642
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,520
She definitely has a son, right?

643
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,160
- Yes.
- That's right.

644
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:19,000
Sorry to bother you.

645
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:21,280
- What are they up to?
- I remember it's a son.

646
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:24,190
Give me back my Xuan!

647
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:27,470
Xuan!

648
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:30,520
My Xuan...

649
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:34,600
Xuan...

650
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:38,150
Give back my Xuan!

651
00:28:38,270 --> 00:28:39,950
My Xuan!

652
00:28:43,370 --> 00:28:44,310
Sir,

653
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,620
is this woman from your village?

654
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,640
Yes.

655
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:51,710
She's Qingniang from our village.

656
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:53,950
Do you know if she has a child?

657
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:55,470
Yes.

658
00:28:55,740 --> 00:28:57,600
She has a four-year-old son.

659
00:28:57,830 --> 00:28:59,430
She talks about him all the time.

660
00:29:01,590 --> 00:29:02,770
- Thanks, sir.
- Thanks, sir.

661
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:06,030
Miss,

662
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,640
is this woman from your village?

663
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:08,950
Yes. I remember her.

664
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:10,840
She often comes
to buy children's clothes.

665
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:12,800
Do you know what her child looks like?

666
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:14,830
About this tall,

667
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,190
with a round face and big eyes.

668
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,910
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

669
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,360
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

670
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,160
Who is it?

671
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:35,600
Master Jingming,
please don't make it hard for me.

672
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:40,000
I won't trouble you.

673
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,950
I'll just stand here

674
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,560
to talk to her.

675
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:44,840
Yes.

676
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:49,920
Jiangli,

677
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:51,600
it's me.

678
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:57,230
Is Yanyan alright?

679
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:59,360
He just wants to see you.

680
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,120
Everything else is fine.

681
00:30:11,590 --> 00:30:13,150
Qingniang is very certain.

682
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,360
Have you ever doubted me?

683
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,360
Never.

684
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:22,630
I promised to protect you and Yanyan.

685
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:26,230
Five years ago,
I trusted others too easily,

686
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,430
which led to you and Yanyan

687
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,230
suffering outside for so long.

688
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:35,600
So this time,

689
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:37,910
no matter what happens,

690
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:40,320
I'll stand by your side.

691
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,520
Please believe me.

692
00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:51,790
♪The night fades away;
I put away my longing♪

693
00:30:52,170 --> 00:30:57,260
♪One only makes one promise
in this one life♪

694
00:30:58,140 --> 00:31:03,380
♪However fast time goes by,
you still wouldn't know my feelings♪

695
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:06,480
♪I can't hold on;
your face is like water♪

696
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:10,950
♪Only your words remain♪

697
00:31:10,950 --> 00:31:15,300
♪Watching the moonlight
gradually disappear on the horizon♪

698
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:21,820
♪There's only an incense stick of time
between us♪

699
00:31:27,910 --> 00:31:29,170
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

700
00:31:29,180 --> 00:31:30,310
We went to Pei Village

701
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:31,600
and interviewed the villagers.

702
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,750
They confirmed Qingniang
indeed had a son,

703
00:31:33,870 --> 00:31:35,320
but he disappeared six months ago.

704
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:36,880
Based on their descriptions,

705
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:37,840
he looks very much

706
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,420
like Young Master Yanyan.

707
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:40,870
It's such a coincidence

708
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,800
as if it was all planned.

709
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:45,000
This is indeed suspicious.

710
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:47,760
Take a team with you

711
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,940
and keep investigating in Pei Village.

712
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:51,710
Talk to more of the older villagers.

713
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:54,320
I'll go see Mr. Chu.

714
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,400
There must be

715
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,560
something I missed.

716
00:31:59,070 --> 00:32:00,030
- Yes.
- Yes.

717
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:10,030
Mr. Chu.

718
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,760
Master Jingming, what's wrong?

719
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,840
Why visit me so late?

720
00:32:15,030 --> 00:32:16,430
I'll speak plainly.

721
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:17,760
Recently,

722
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:18,910
a woman has come here,

723
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:20,440
and she insists

724
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,600
that Yanyan is her son.

725
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,470
The details she provided

726
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:26,000
match Yanyan perfectly.

727
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,670
I sent people to investigate

728
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:29,000
but found no flaws.

729
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,910
This is your family matter,

730
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,430
so I couldn't interfere.

731
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,950
I remember you once said

732
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:39,670
that five years ago

733
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,430
when Jiangli was pregnant,

734
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:44,310
it was you who brought her
to Wind Pavilion

735
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:45,350
and ensured

736
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:47,040
her and Yanyan's safety.

737
00:32:47,960 --> 00:32:49,040
So now,

738
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:51,040
only you and Wind Pavilion

739
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:52,870
can prove their innocence.

740
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:56,520
You know there's no peace
in the Prefect's Mansion.

741
00:32:56,750 --> 00:32:57,590
Everyone

742
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:59,120
has their agenda.

743
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,360
I'm afraid that in Dongzhou,

744
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:03,360
only you and I

745
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,080
want to ensure their safety.

746
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:08,840
So,

747
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,600
you believe her?

748
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,400
Five years ago,

749
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,280
because I didn't trust her,

750
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:19,080
she suffered at the ancestral tomb.

751
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:21,670
But today,

752
00:33:22,830 --> 00:33:24,120
no matter what others say

753
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:25,950
or present as evidence,

754
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,430
I only believe Shen Jiangli.

755
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:39,680
You're no longer the same

756
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:40,600
as five years ago.

757
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:43,040
It seems Jiangli made the right choice

758
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:43,960
by staying.

759
00:33:44,350 --> 00:33:45,200
Let's go.

760
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,360
I'll go with you.

761
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:48,680
Please.

762
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:55,500
(Prefect's Mansion)

763
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,670
- Greetings.
- Greetings.

764
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:00,520
This is Mr. Chu.

765
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:03,000
We are investigating it
by the Prefect's orders.

766
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:04,520
- Yes.
- Yes.

767
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,080
Stay away.

768
00:34:10,590 --> 00:34:12,190
Give me back my child!

769
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:13,920
Stay away!

770
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:15,030
Don't be afraid.

771
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:17,020
We're here to help you find your child.

772
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,030
Xuan...

773
00:34:23,030 --> 00:34:23,990
Qingniang,

774
00:34:24,190 --> 00:34:25,230
this isn't a bad man.

775
00:34:25,510 --> 00:34:26,560
This is Mr. Chu.

776
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,440
Please tell him again

777
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:29,880
when and where

778
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:31,040
your Xuan

779
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:32,150
went missing.

780
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:36,630
Six months ago,

781
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,710
I brought Xuan to Dongzhou for fun.

782
00:34:39,230 --> 00:34:41,630
He said he wanted to row a boat,

783
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:44,600
so we came to Ping Lake.

784
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:47,190
I told him to wait at the pavilion,

785
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,040
while I went to find the boatman.

786
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:51,310
But when I came back,

787
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,960
my Xuan

788
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,480
was gone.

789
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,480
My Xuan is gone...

790
00:34:57,190 --> 00:34:58,960
My Xuan is gone...

791
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,830
Give me back my Xuan!

792
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:04,230
Give me back my child!

793
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:05,750
My Xuan!

794
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,840
My Lord,

795
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:10,190
Qingniang has been crying
every day in the mansion.

796
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:12,000
If word of this gets out,

797
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:14,560
it'll damage our family's reputation.

798
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:15,960
My Lord,

799
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,630
you need to make a decision quickly.

800
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,440
Father,

801
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,440
I've investigated the truth behind this.

802
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:28,040
What exactly happened?

803
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:30,510
Are you trying to create false evidence

804
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,000
to exonerate your wife?

805
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:33,030
Father,

806
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:34,230
please bring everyone involved

807
00:35:34,230 --> 00:35:35,480
to the hall,

808
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:36,550
and I will

809
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,600
reveal the truth.

810
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,760
Okay.

811
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:39,720
You have my permission.

812
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,720
Don't be afraid.

813
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,400
Where's Yanyan?

814
00:35:58,840 --> 00:36:00,110
There's too much going on today.

815
00:36:00,110 --> 00:36:01,880
I've arranged for Yanyan
to stay at home.

816
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,360
Jingming,

817
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,670
what's really going on?

818
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,790
Tell us then.

819
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,520
Xuan, Xuan.

820
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,280
Xuan...

821
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:31,150
What's going on here?

822
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:33,750
She didn't recognize
any other child that day.

823
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,320
Because Qingniang

824
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,400
didn't recognize a person

825
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:38,840
but attire.

826
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:39,800
That day,

827
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,750
Yanyan's uniform

828
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:43,230
was different from usual.

829
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:45,830
The cloud-patterned belt
around his waist

830
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,590
was of a style and color

831
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:49,410
that didn't match
our family's usual attire.

832
00:36:49,450 --> 00:36:50,960
- Don't be afraid.
- Someone must've

833
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:51,920
tampered with it.

834
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:53,150
What?

835
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,120
- I'm here.
- Mr. Song.

836
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:56,760
Yes.

837
00:36:58,150 --> 00:36:59,110
Xuan.

838
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,270
Don't be afraid. Let me see.

839
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,720
My Lord,

840
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,920
this belt

841
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:17,880
is indeed different from the one

842
00:37:18,030 --> 00:37:19,270
I had someone send

843
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,400
to the mansion.

844
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:22,000
How bold

845
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,750
to tamper under my nose!

846
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:26,550
Bring him here.

847
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,920
Mr. Song, please save me.

848
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,710
It was a momentary lapse.

849
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,630
You scoundrel!

850
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,480
You've disgraced me completely!

851
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,630
Tell the Prefect everything

852
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:41,600
you did now!

853
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,400
Tell us the truth.

854
00:38:03,491 --> 00:38:07,251
♪The sound of the flute lingers,
making the night more tender♪

855
00:38:07,621 --> 00:38:11,321
♪Stealing a bit of the starry sky,
making the encounter romantic♪

856
00:38:11,921 --> 00:38:15,471
♪The lights fade; the story isn't over♪

857
00:38:15,721 --> 00:38:19,241
♪Let's continue our fate♪

858
00:38:20,861 --> 00:38:24,831
♪A cup of wine
to honor courage and love's trials♪

859
00:38:25,041 --> 00:38:28,951
♪For you, I'd dare to travel,
however long the journey is♪

860
00:38:29,331 --> 00:38:32,991
♪The world's many twists
end in separation♪

861
00:38:33,171 --> 00:38:36,851
♪I can't bear to watch♪

862
00:38:37,551 --> 00:38:42,001
